<section>
<title>Detailed Description</title>

<para>Main controller class implementing Blackjack game logic. </para>



<para>This class implements the Singleton pattern and manages the complete lifecycle of a Blackjack game including player turns, dealer actions, betting, and game state persistence. </para>
